    • applyForProject

      public void applyForProject(Applicant applicant, IApplicantProjectService projectService)
      Allows the applicant to apply for a project they are eligible for. Prompts the user to select a project and flat type (if they are married), validates input, and creates the application. There are also checks for whether the applicant has a pending application, if they're reapplying for the same project they were unsuccessful for, and for flat availability before allowing the application.
      Specified by:
      applyForProject in interface IApplicantApplicationService
      Parameters:
      applicant - The applicant who is applying for a project.
      projectService - The project service used to retrieve list of projects to apply for
